Paper: hep-th/9403005

Date: 1994-03-01

Title: Symmetries of the Kadomstev-Petviashvili Hierarchy

Authors: A. Yu. Orlov and P. Winternitz

Comments: 4 pages, CRM-2149

The relation between the $\widehat{\Sl}(\infty)$ algebra of flows commutingwith the KP hierarchy and the Kac-Moody-Virasoro Lie point symmetries ofindividual equations is established. This is used to calculate the pointsymmetries for all equations in the hierarchy.